        },
        "subject": "LU-4701 osp: OSP object attributes cache cleanup",
        "message": "LU-4701 osp: OSP object attributes cache cleanup\n\n1) Some adjustment for OSP object attributes cache maintainig to make\n   the logic more clear and reasonable.\n1.1) Update the cached attribute in osp_attr_set(), but not in the\n     osp_declare_attr_set().\n1.2) Update the cached extended attribute in osp_xattr_set(), but not\n     in the osp_declare_xattr_set().\n1.3) Drop the cached extended attribute in osp_xattr_del().\n\n2) Typo fixing and code cleanup.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ic7e96abec2a8bc3d30859b6f3a0a6b4d26222104\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
